    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka: Fugitive Gotabhaya Rajapaksa, Struggle and Current Crisis",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Gotabhaya Rajapakse, who escaped to Maldives in a military plane, left for Singapore from Mal\u00e9, the capital of Maldives.",
        "It is SV788 belonging to Saudi Arabian Airlines which left from Velana International Airport in Maldives to Singapore this morning.",
        "Meanwhile, the activists continue to demand that Ranil Wickramasinghe, who has been sworn in as the Acting President after the resignation of President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa, resign immediately."
      ],
